---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Worship — Weekly Prayer Plan"
  description="A full weekly prayer plan that rotates through seven distinct postures — Ask, Study, Intercede, Bless, Repent, Praise, and Meditate — each with a descriptive guide and reflection questions."
>
  <div class="takeaways-content pp-page">
    <span class="takeaways-tag">Worship</span>
    <h1 class="takeaways-title">Weekly Prayer Plan</h1>
    <p class="pp-subtitle">Seven postures. One complete prayer life.</p>

    <div class="pp-grid">

      <!-- MONDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-monday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Monday</h2>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Ask</div>
        </div>
        <p class="pp-guide">Set aside time for quiet, focused prayer, seeking God's direct intervention in your life. Begin by surrendering distractions and opening your heart to the Holy Spirit's leading. Present your personal needs, desires, and concerns to God with open hands, trusting in His provision and protection. Seek wisdom and discernment for decisions, and pray for genuine heart transformation. Conclude by listening for His gentle promptings and jotting down any insights.</p>
        <div class="pp-steps">
          <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>What's one area where I'm longing for God to move in my own life?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Where do I need God's wisdom and discernment in my current circumstances?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>What area of my heart do I need God to transform?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Lord, what do You want me to take away from this time?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-footer">
          <a href="/worship/prayer-guides/monday-ask/" class="pp-deeper-btn">Open Prayer Prompts →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- TUESDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-tuesday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Tuesday</h2>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Study</div>
        </div>
        <p class="pp-guide">Read one scripture passage slowly, jotting down questions, key words, commands, etc. Use commentary to understand the historical background, cultural context, and deeper meaning of the passage. Identify key themes and truths, then select a verse to commit to memory. Allow these words to resonate throughout your day, shaping your thoughts and perspectives. Reflect on the passage, and invite God to embed its message within your heart and guide you in its application.</p>
        <div class="pp-steps">
          <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>What is the author trying to communicate?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>What questions do I have that commentary might help with?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Which specific verse will I practice reciting throughout my day?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>How can the key message shape my thoughts, decisions, or attitudes this week?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-footer">
          <a href="/worship/prayer-guides/tuesday-study/" class="pp-deeper-btn">Open Bible Study Guide →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- WEDNESDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-wednesday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Wednesday</h2>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Intercede</div>
        </div>
        <p class="pp-guide">Expand your prayer focus today to intercede for others, encompassing your personal circle, your community, and the wider world. Lift up specific individuals, including leaders, missionaries, and those facing persecution. Pray scriptural promises over these groups, asking God to move powerfully in their lives and circumstances. If you feel compelled, send a text to check in on their prayer requests, and let them know you prayed.</p>
        <div class="pp-steps">
          <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Who is facing a spiritual battle or needs breakthrough?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Who is experiencing relational pain or needs healing?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Who needs provision, protection, or guidance through a crisis?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Name one area in the world where I'm longing for God to move.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-footer">
          <a href="/worship/prayer-guides/wednesday-intercede/" class="pp-deeper-btn">Open Intercession Inventory →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- THURSDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-thursday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Thursday</h2>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Bless</div>
        </div>
        <p class="pp-guide">Focus today on actively extending God's grace and love to others. Think of several acts of service, thoughtful gifts, or words of affirmation that you could offer that reflect Christ's servant heart. Then ask the Holy Spirit for courage to initiate, humility to serve quietly, and wisdom to bless in ways that are actually helpful. Let your prayers fuel these actions, and allow these actions to deepen your prayer life, reinforcing your commitment to living out your faith.</p>
        <div class="pp-steps">
          <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>How can I help carry someone else's burden and walk alongside them today?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>How can I better reflect God's unconditional love to those who are difficult to love?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Who needs what I have (time, money, knowledge, influence, skills) right now?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>If Jesus physically walked into my day today, where would He go, and who would He stop for?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-footer">
          <a href="/worship/prayer-guides/thursday-bless/" class="pp-deeper-btn">Open Blessing Guide →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- FRIDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-friday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Friday</h2>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Repent</div>
        </div>
        <p class="pp-guide">Approach God with humility today, acknowledging and confessing areas where you have fallen short. Kneel or bow in prayer, honestly naming pride, selfishness, or any other sin that has hindered your relationship with Him or others. Ask for both forgiveness and transformation, trusting in His boundless mercy. Commit to a specific, tangible change this week, relying on His power to renew your heart and guide you toward an opposite act of obedience.</p>
        <div class="pp-steps">
          <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Where have I relied on my own wisdom instead of trusting God's lead?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>How has my pride, selfishness, or judgment wounded someone I was meant to love?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>When did I opt for comfort or distraction over wholehearted devotion?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Is there a conversation, confession, or confrontation I'm avoiding?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-footer">
          <a href="/worship/prayer-guides/friday-repent/" class="pp-deeper-btn">Open Repentance Guide →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- SATURDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-saturday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Saturday</h2>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Praise</div>
        </div>
        <p class="pp-guide">Think back on your week and choose three moments: one highlight, one struggle, and one ordinary instance. For each, consider how God was at work — whether protecting, providing, teaching, or refining you. Then make two lists side by side: on the left, write specific things you're thankful for ("Thank You for..."); on the right, write what each blessing shows you about who God is ("I praise You because You are..."). End by thanking Him for being present in both the peaks and the valleys.</p>
        <div class="pp-steps">
          <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>What blessing from this week am I most grateful for?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>In what ways has God met my needs or answered my prayers recently?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>What's one complaint from this week I can let go of and replace with a thankful heart?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Which attribute or name of God am I most drawn to as I reflect on the week?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-footer">
          <a href="/worship/prayer-guides/saturday-praise/" class="pp-deeper-btn">Open Gratitude Inventory →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- SUNDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-sunday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Sunday</h2>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Meditate</div>
        </div>
        <p class="pp-guide">Embrace a day of intentional worship and restorative rest. Seek the Lord's presence at church as you sing, take communion, and listen to the reading of the word. Then commit to observing the Sabbath by replacing digital habits with life-giving activities such as reading, journaling, spending time in nature, or engaging in meaningful conversations. Practice saying "no" to productivity and "yes" to savoring God's presence and creation.</p>
        <div class="pp-steps">
          <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>What song lyric or Scripture verse stood out to me during church or quiet time?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Which unfinished tasks or distractions is the Holy Spirit inviting me to rest from today?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>What does "restorative rest" look like for my soul, mind, and body right now?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pp-step">
            <p>Where in nature can I savor God's presence and creation today?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-footer">
          <a href="/worship/prayer-guides/sunday-meditate/" class="pp-deeper-btn">Open Sabbath Devotional →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div><!-- /.pp-grid -->

  </div><!-- /.takeaways-content -->
</BaseLayout>

<style>
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

/* ── Page wrapper ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.pp-page {
  max-width: 1040px;
  padding-top: 2rem;
}

/* ── Subtitle ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.pp-subtitle {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #7a7368;
  margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ── Card grid ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.pp-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}

/* ── Individual card ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
.pp-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  border: 1px solid rgba(199, 187, 170, 0.45);
  border-left: 3px solid #c2a86d;
  border-radius: 6px;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
}

.pp-card:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 5px 22px rgba(70, 61, 52, 0.1);
}

/* ── Card header ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.pp-card-top {
  padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem 1rem;
  background: rgba(183, 156, 92, 0.07);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(183, 156, 92, 0.15);
}

.pp-day {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #3d3830;
  margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.pp-mode-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #b79c5c;
  background: rgba(183, 156, 92, 0.13);
  border: 1px solid rgba(183, 156, 92, 0.3);
  padding: 0.22rem 0.65rem;
  border-radius: 2px;
}

/* ── Guide paragraph ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
.pp-guide {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 0.93rem;
  color: #5e554b;
  line-height: 1.65;
  font-style: italic;
  padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
  background: rgba(233, 227, 216, 0.4);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(199, 187, 170, 0.3);
  margin: 0;
}

.pp-guide::before {
  content: 'Guide';
  display: block;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.56rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-style: normal;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #b79c5c;
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
}

/* ── Reflect steps ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.pp-steps {
  padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0;
  flex: 1;
}

.pp-reflect-label {
  display: block;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.56rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #b79c5c;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.pp-step {
  padding: 0.7rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(199, 187, 170, 0.25);
}

.pp-step:first-of-type {
  padding-top: 0;
}

.pp-step:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
  padding-bottom: 0;
}

.pp-step p {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: #5e554b;
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin: 0;
}

/* ── Card footer / deeper button ─────────────────────────────── */
.pp-card-footer {
  padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem 1rem;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(199, 187, 170, 0.25);
}

.pp-deeper-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #b79c5c;
  border: 1px solid rgba(183, 156, 92, 0.45);
  border-radius: 3px;
  padding: 0.4rem 0.85rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
}

.pp-deeper-btn:hover {
  background: rgba(183, 156, 92, 0.12);
  color: #8a6f30;
  border-color: rgba(183, 156, 92, 0.65);
}

/* ── Responsive: tablet → 1 column ───────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .pp-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}

/* ── Responsive: mobile refinements ──────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .pp-day {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .pp-card-top {
    padding: 0.9rem 1rem 0.85rem;
  }

  .pp-guide,
  .pp-steps {
    padding-left: 1rem;
    padding-right: 1rem;
  }
}
</style>
